Title: Girls can travel the world alone
DateModified: '2019-03-11'
DatePublished: '2019-03-11'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/girls-can-travel-the-world-alone
SetInCountry: Egypt
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Mariam Abdelmalak
AuthorCountry: Egypt
Text: My story about a girl that wants to travel the world exploring new things ,
  she believe that she can survive on her own. She wants to encourage girls to travel
  to gain new experience and learn about new different cultures and countries. Although
  she still a college girl at the age of twenth that wants to enjoy her summer vacation,
  learn new things and make her dream became true.
